# - Config file for the mctools package
# It defines the following variables
#  mctools_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories for mctools
#  mctools_LIBRARY      - libraries to link against
#  mctools_BIO_LIBRARY  - library targets to link against (Boost I/O library)
#  mctools_REFLECTION_LIBRARY - library targets to link against (reflection library)
#  mctools_LIBRARIES    - libraries to link against
#  mctools_WITH_BIO     - flag for Boost/Serialization I/O DLL (a.k.a. 'bio')
#  mctools_WITH_REFLECTION  - flag for reflection DLL
#  mctools_WITH_G4      - flag for Geant4 interface

